#{129}{}{I lived in Spring Valley then. I walked back home the other night, from my friend's house. We drank a little, as usual... And then - a bright light from the sky! Blinded me - and suddenly I lost consciousness, I think these aliens stunned me with some sound. I woke up on a strange frame, bound, covered in wires...}
{129}{}{我那时住在春谷。那天晚上我从朋友家走回家。我们像往常一样喝了一点。。。然后-天空中一道亮光！把我弄瞎了-突然我失去了知觉，我想这些外星人用一些声音把我惊呆了。我在一个陌生的框架上醒来，被绑着，浑身是电线。。。 -- I lived in Spring Valley then. I walked back home the other night, from my friend's house. We drank a little, as usual... And then - a bright light from the sky! Blinded me - and suddenly I lost consciousness, I think these aliens stunned me with some sound. I woke up on a strange frame, bound, covered in wires...}
#{130}{}{Drank a little? Oh, this explains a lot. Go on, weirdo.}
{130}{}{喝了一点？哦，这解释了很多。去吧，怪人。 -- Drank a little? Oh, this explains a lot. Go on, weirdo.}
#{131}{}{Not the most pleasant awakening, sorry... What happened next?}
{131}{}{不是最愉快的觉醒，对不起。。。接下来发生了什么？ -- Not the most pleasant awakening, sorry... What happened next?}
#{132}{}{[Shakes, hugging himself around shoulders] Then the most terrible things began... They did some experiments, stuck needles in me, cut off a piece here and there, forced me to swallow some nasty stuff... They opened my skull without anesthesia! Did you ever hear the crunching of your own skull?! I screamed so hard...}
{132}{}{[颤抖，搂着肩膀]然后最可怕的事情开始了。。。他们做了一些实验，把针扎在我身上，到处切下一块，强迫我吞下一些恶心的东西。。。他们在没有麻醉的情况下打开了我的头骨！你有没有听过自己脑袋的嘎吱声？！我尖叫得很厉害。。。 -- [Shakes, hugging himself around shoulders] Then the most terrible things began... They did some experiments, stuck needles in me, cut off a piece here and there, forced me to swallow some nasty stuff... They opened my skull without anesthesia! Did you ever hear the crunching of your own skull?! I screamed so hard...}
#{133}{}{What a creative approach! Who was it, so skillful?}
{133}{}{多有创意的方法啊！是谁，这么熟练？ -- What a creative approach! Who was it, so skillful?}
#{134}{}{It is difficult even to imagine this, my friend... And "they" - who are they? Did you see them?}
