#{135}{}{I... I'm not sure. What I saw was - my vision was blurry - only two gray silhouettes, swaying. And I didn17t hear them talking - instead, some weird cricketing... I couldn't even spit in their faces - they sewn my mouth up... But I did even better! I ran away from them! [Laughing hoarsely] Oh, that was great.}
{135}{}{一、 。。。我不确定。我看到的是-我的视线模糊-只有两个灰色的轮廓，摇摆。我没听见他们说话-相反，一些奇怪的板球。。。我甚至不能在他们脸上吐痰-他们把我的嘴缝起来。。。但我做得更好！我逃离了他们！哦，太棒了。 -- I... I'm not sure. What I saw was - my vision was blurry - only two gray silhouettes, swaying. And I didn17t hear them talking - instead, some weird cricketing... I couldn't even spit in their faces - they sewn my mouth up... But I did even better! I ran away from them! [Laughing hoarsely] Oh, that was great.}
#{136}{}{Uh-huh, sure. Looks like they just threw you away after using.}
