#{137}{}{Really?! How did you do that? It must have been something very extraordinary!}
{137}{}{真正地？！你是怎么做到的？一定是很特别的事！ -- Really?! How did you do that? It must have been something very extraordinary!}
#{138}{}{They dragged me somewhere outside... In the wasteland... Dropped me on the ground. They probably thought that a piece of meat I turned into won't be dangerous anymore. Just one of them stayed with me... I lunged at him, clung into his slimy head and crushed it like a rotten mutafruit! A fountain of green ooze sprayed me whole... And then I crawled... For a long, long time...}
{138}{}{他们把我拖到外面某个地方。。。在荒地里。。。把我扔在地上。他们可能认为我做的一块肉不会再危险了。只有一个和我在一起。。。我向他猛扑过去，紧紧抓住他黏糊糊的脑袋，像一颗腐烂的果子一样把它压碎了！一股绿色的软泥喷了我一身。。。然后我爬。。。很久很久了。。。 -- They dragged me somewhere outside... In the wasteland... Dropped me on the ground. They probably thought that a piece of meat I turned into won't be dangerous anymore. Just one of them stayed with me... I lunged at him, clung into his slimy head and crushed it like a rotten mutafruit! A fountain of green ooze sprayed me whole... And then I crawled... For a long, long time...}
