#{142}{}{Words, words, words... 15 minutes of wasted life, no weapon, no sense. Farewell, wacko.}
{142}{}{言语，言语，言语。。。浪费了15分钟的生命，没有武器，没有意义。再见，怪人。 -- Words, words, words... 15 minutes of wasted life, no weapon, no sense. Farewell, wacko.}
